<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Third-Party Licenses</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; max-width: 900px; margin: 2em auto; padding: 0 1em; color: #222; line-height: 1.5; }
  h1 { border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: 0.3em; }
  h2, h3 { margin-top: 2em; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc; padding-bottom: 0.3em; }
  .license-text { background: #f7f7f7; padding: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; font-size: 0.82em; border-radius: 6px; overflow-x: auto; max-height: 30em; overflow-y: auto; }
  ul.crates { columns: 2; column-gap: 2em; list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  ul.crates li { break-inside: avoid; padding: 0.1em 0; }
  ul.overview li { padding: 0.2em 0; }
  details { margin: 0.5em 0; }
  summary { cursor: pointer; color: #555; user-select: none; }
  a { color: #0366d6; text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Third-Party Licenses</h1>
<p>This software bundles third-party Rust crates under the following licenses.
Full license texts are included below.</p>

<h2>Overview</h2>
<ul class="overview">
{{#each overview}}
  <li><a href="#{{id}}"><strong>{{name}}</strong></a> — {{count}} crate(s)</li>
{{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Licenses</h2>
{{#each licenses}}
<h3 id="{{id}}">{{name}}</h3>
<details open>
<summary>Crates</summary>
<ul class="crates">
{{#each used_by}}
  <li>{{this.crate.name}} <small>{{this.crate.version}}</small></li>
{{/each}}
</ul>
</details>
<details>
<summary>License text</summary>
<pre class="license-text">{{text}}</pre>
</details>
{{/each}}

</body>
</html>
